Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.74,0:00:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the contract is signed, Kosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, you will become\Nthe Magical Pâtissière Kosaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and help bring about peace\Nfor everyone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand! Rurin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait, I forgot to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During the few seconds that you're transforming\Ninto the Magical Pâtissière, you'll be stark naked,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't mind, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? What did you\Njust say? Stark naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! We're going to go\Nsave people in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I was just thinking,\Nthis is going to be an ordeal...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:00:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:12.33,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Pâtissière Kosaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you, isn't it about time you stopped running\Ninto the bathroom every time you transform?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just go naked in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares, really?\NNot like it's detrimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes it is! Very!\NTo my mental health!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can transform any time,\Nanywhere with this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now get yourself transformed! Kosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's still no good, Rurin! You can still see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic, Magical Pâtissière!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you're fit\Nto serve as a Magical Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:05.59,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you this city's resident Magical Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you're capable of safeguarding\Nall the love and peace in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Magical Girl of Love,\Nguardian of the peace of the next town over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Marika Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean there are\Nother magical girls besides me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please... you don't have to\Nsay it so matter-of-factly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Acting so mortified every time you transform...\Nyou can't call yourself a full-fledged magical girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall show you how\Na real magical girl transforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:56.47,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Police Marika is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Police Marika - is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do? This girl\Ndoesn't have a shred of shame!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take a page out her book, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.77,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your fellow magical girls\Nshould all be here in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you were so gung-ho\Nwhen you signed the contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Magical Gorilla Chitoge?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is a Magical Gorilla!?\NIt's not the least bit cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was, hoping for more magical girl-y,\Nall frills and ribbons and adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I think you look adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Liar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since a magical girl's costume takes\Nthe form of that girl's secret talents,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, being able to pulverize concrete\Nwith a flick of my forehead was a surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we've got to find\Nthe other magical girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure, we need to find them,\Nbut a cat talking in the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's too conspicuous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then should I assume my human form?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean you can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Since it's a necessary skill\Nfor blending in with the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right... transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you get a cuter costume than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No fair! No fair! Trade me! Trade me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's easy enough for you to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:44.46,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to assemble\Nin this town for one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, I want you three\Nto work as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To take on the evil minions\Nwho've been on a rampage of late,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to have to join\Nforces and give it your best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in that case, you can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to have comrades!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wonder if they'll be my friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you decide on your leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we're talking about leaders,\Nbased on ability and experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,surely there's no question\Nthat I should be the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be the leader, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.59,DefaultMid2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Handle With Care
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You only just became a magical girl\Nthe other day, you little newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have\Nto do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, let's play fair\Nand decide via rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no, I won!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but just because I'm the leader now, it\Ndoesn't mean I get special privileges or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, whenever you announce yourselves\Nto the enemy, you always get the center position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from that, in any and all situations, you get to\Nmonopolize the coolest lines and signature poses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though you do have other trivial tasks, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't it be me who serves\Nas our leader after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean by other trivial tasks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No biggie, just some simple admin work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First, you're to write up a weekly report on\Nyour team activities and submit it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As the Magical Girl HQ will be basing their\Nfuture policies for our team on these reports,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,make sure they're accurate and reader-friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The leader is also in charge of\Nall team members' expense reports,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you need to stay on top\Nof all necessary receipts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be expected to indicate clearly\Nwhose expense and what it was for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We may be magical girls, but our share\Nof the operational budget is paltry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss any deductions, you'll regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, since all complaints and requests\Nfrom the local residents go through HQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you need to keep a constant eye\Non whatever's in our jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to head over to the Magic Ward Office\Nto have the paperwork for our team processed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Later, after you've collected each member's\Nproof of residence and some form of ID,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,go to the Magical Ward Office and apply at the\NMagical Girl New Applications window...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? Not so hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really a magical girl's job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank goodness I'm not the leader!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:12.77,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:22.03,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An evil minion has appeared in Bonyari City!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All magical girls in this area, report at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! We're totally overmatched!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't possibly defeat something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, you can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this, our only hope is\Nto join forces and use our killer move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Killer move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... The only thing is, to use it,\Ncertain stringent conditions must be met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:09:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you must stand stark naked for five\Nminutes, and concentrate all your magical powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Five minutes during\Na battle will feel far too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's probably crucial, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why stark naked!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's a killer move that packs and unleashes\Nevery ounce of your magical powers, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to use the power of those\Nmagical costumes of yours as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Standing here in public for five minutes\Nlike that... we'd only look like perverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. If you don't hurry,\Nthere's only going to be more havoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a pair of wimps.\NI don't mind in the least!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured. In the meantime,\NI'll draw the enemy in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? By yourself, Rurin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I can't let you three\Nbe the only ones to face danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can fight, too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Extreme Total Defensive Magic,\Nable to withstand even a nuclear blast...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and my Super-Extreme Invincible\NAttack Magic, able to wipe out small planets,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will surely stop the enemy in its tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then doesn't that mean\Nyou don't need us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:13.56,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Small planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder they call it\Na killer move when we join forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sheer force was incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, Leader, Gorilla!\NLet's get out of here, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you for defeating\Nmy minion, magical girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard rumors several promising magic girls\Narrived in this town, so I came to take a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly look as advertised, rookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Dr. Maikou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, Rurin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Know him? He's the one who unleashed\Nall those evil minions on the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The evil scientist plotting\Nworld domination... Dr. Maikou himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the master of evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Dr. Maikou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you do such evil things?\NI mean, world domination...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I do them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in world domination!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I'm gunning for\Nworld domination, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is because I want to battle the magical girls who\Ncome to stop me from dominating the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, magical girls are all pretty girls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You get to see them looking sexy while they\Ntransform, you get to see their pretty costumes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's not to love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And since those magical girls seem happy to attack\Nme in an endless stream, well, sure, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky me for being born a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have to take him out. No matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.16,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go, magical girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you can soundly defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I can't\Nget that pumped up about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the big boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, let's just\Nmake short work of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! Dr. Maikou's new weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Neutralizing Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did it take you by surprise, perhaps?\NThe destructive power of this beam?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This beam can't be blocked\Nby those clothes made of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-What's up\Nwith that? That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, our only option is to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With my Magic Cuffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that it can\Nobliterate any kind of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Tachibana! In front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, let's un-transform for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't win in our current forms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what are we going to do?\NThere's nothing we can do like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! My hand somehow slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you guys, let's\Nhead back to our hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he's here, we've got to\Ncome up with our next strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.00,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This work is fiction. It is not related to any\Nactual living things, groups and locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura can't make it on Sunday, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kato said she couldn't come, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now I'm in a bind. Losing two staff\Nmembers so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll work at the shop, too!\NSister, you're going in too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd still be short one person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaki, can you ask that boy\Nfrom the other day to pitch in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Sure, okay! I'll try asking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pitch in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there you are, young lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Work!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Ichijo the one pitching in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's pitched in before, he has\Nexperience, and Mom acknowledges his skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I just cover what he'd be doing,\Nwe wouldn't need him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need anyone to pitch in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't tell him that now, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he's already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy... the nerve of him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he's been going after\Nmy sister for that long, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But as long as I'm here, I won't\Nlet him lay a finger on my sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ugh... she's totally on red alert...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But since she's Onodera's kid sister,\NI really wish we could be friends...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:15:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like things are tense\Nbetween Haru and Ichijo, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really wish those two could be friends...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Haru, are you\Nalready buddies with Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaki! Seems like you have a rival now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Mom!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, why don't we get to work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start like we did last time,\Nby making the bean paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, would you mind handing\Nme that teaspoon there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... uh... Haru, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have all these\Nmisunderstandings about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Misunderstandings?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, what could you be referring to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you saw my underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I do think that\Nthat's an indisputable fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you have to talk about\Nthat in front of Onodera?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I supposed to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom asked me to run an errand\Nfor her, so I'll be out for a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to Haru, it didn't seem like\NIchijo meant to see her underwear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure if they talk it out...\Nthey can become friends, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}N-No way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I thought I could\Nspend the day with Onodera!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How very unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You being deprived of your target - my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually impressed that you\Nhad the guts to appear before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After the horrible thing you did to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? I told you, that wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you had to do was avert your gaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But no, you even offered your comments...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well, I admit that was wrong, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to spell it out\Nvery clearly for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever try to go\Nnear my sister again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I find most\Nunforgivable about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is the fact that you're trying\Nto make a play for my sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when you already have\Nsuch a gorgeous girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of nerve is that?\NAs a person, you're the lowest of the low!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that my sister is pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but she's also a pure,\Nfeminine, ultra-lovely big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. On top of that she's gentle,\Nand has so much empathy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You're absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind to anyone she meets,\Nand she has an especially lovely smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She sure does! I don't know how many\Ntimes that smile has saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the way she's such a klutz\Nonce in a while... that's adorable, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind not jumping onto\Nmy bandwagon without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely why I can't stand the thought of\Nhanding her over to an insincere man like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This kid must really love Onodera.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not quite the same, but I\Nknow too well how that feels...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although it's so uncool to bring it up myself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really shouldn't be so hard on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who saved you from those thugs\Ncrowding you the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Setting aside the underwear incident,\Nand whatever rumors you've heard about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you at least hear me out a little...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!? What the heck are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I already knew you were\Nthe lowest of the low...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I never thought you'd go\Nso far as to tarnish my prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How corrupt is that soul of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't really remember\Nanything about that prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell right away that it wasn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, no, hold up! I really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,According to my hazy memories...\NHe was at least 180 cm tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He had a face like a Hollywood star,\Nand a clear voice like a voice actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's embellished my image!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you'd try to\Nwin me over with a lie like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're rotten to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, that's not what I meant to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no good. If I say\Nany more, it'll only backfire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I was wrong, okay?\NJust forget what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bet I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say creepy things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe he'd tell a horrible lie like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are all men like that, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's just start over and get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just curl up in some corner somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just right, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you seem to be\Npretty good, Haru. At cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since it seems like it's\Nnot Onodera's strong point...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's just because my sister\Nhappens to be special.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been like that\Nsince I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was the one they trained in her place,\Nand the one who helped out in the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of course I'm the one who can do all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watching you work, Haru, I can tell that\Nyou really love making Japanese sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way you handle your tools,\Nthe way each and every step is so polished...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the sweets you make are really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could taste some!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you offer such blatant lip service,\Nit doesn't make me happy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm gonna help out, after all.\NI'll take care not to get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's all right, you'd only be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way he moves... it's not amateurish.\NHe really knows what he's doing... and it's really...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you make them at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese sweets...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A lot, these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I got to work here\Nthe last time, I've really gotten into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying out stuff on my own.\NJapanese sweets are totally deep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I see. Not that it matters anyway...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And besides, it's not like what he makes\Ncould possibly taste good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yum! This exquisite degree\Nof sweetness and silky-smooth texture...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's not good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not good at all, you know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? I did use the daifuku\Nsweets from Suzumiya as a reference...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Did you say Suzumiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I really love their daifuku, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've got some amazing\Nfine-grained paste, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The balance between sweetness\Nand slight saltiness is so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really love their strawberry daifuku!\NThey're the best, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, those rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:22:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since they use quality strawberries...\NThat juiciness is to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think whoever was the first to put\Nstrawberries inside a daifuku was a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said it! You could even call it\Na game-changer in human history!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I know exactly what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What am I doing,\Nhaving a blast talking to this guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy is my enemy!\NHe's the enemy, got that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, now I'm starting to crave some!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You two are alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's unusual for you,\Nmy little man-hater, Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haru! Don't come running to me\Nif you have to fight over him with your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? Who would ever...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's the same as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who... who would ever fall for this guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that's enough!\NPlease go off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But no, I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... That's too heavy for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, where do you\Nthink you're touching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, if I let go now it'll all fall over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At least leave the heavy stuff to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.71,0:23:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am a guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A... a guy? A guy? What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle this by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. Stay still, will you? It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.34,0:23:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't cut it out, I'm going\Nto yell as loud as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So loud my sister will hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Go ahead. It would be\Na lot worse if you got injured because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where's that coming from?\NSuch a grating line as that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guys' hands are so burly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never knew they were so big...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Looks like you got\Ncloser than I thought, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.58,0:23:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you just let go like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.63,0:23:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the... What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Didn't I tell you to be careful!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way am I going to let my\Nguard down against you, all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're going to pay for this,\Ngot that!? I hope you're prepared!
